payload.reasoning: The goal was to draft a concise 5-item checklist; no command execution was needed.
payload.result:
- Finalize build: bump version, update changelog/release notes, sign/notarize, produce artifacts.
- Validate: CI green, QA/regression pass, security scan, smoke test install/upgrade.
- Prep release: update store metadata (description, screenshots), docs, migration notes.
- Plan rollout: choose staged/percent rollout, schedule window, notify stakeholders, define rollback.
- Launch & monitor: release, watch metrics/crashes, track support/feedback, hotfix if needed.
